item.description:
Way over to KEEN for coffee, eggs, homefries and sausage.

Breakfast Fly out... We decided the pilots and helpers for the Young Eagles event needed an update on what's happening for Sunday..... So.......we decided to fly for eggs first, then meet at Bullocks after. (Or the back room of FCA where we have AC if needed)

 

Those not able or wanting to fly (WHAT?) can meet us after to discuss the updated info for Young Eagles.

 

Fly Often and Fly Safe (yup)

Charley
